<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN:
    <li>questDescription->[asker_nameFull], a [asker_royalTitleInCurrentFaction] of [asker_faction_name] is calling from nearby. [asker_pronoun] is being followed by an angry [animalKindDef_label]! [asker_pronoun] says [asker_pronoun] only wanted to see the landscape on a quick walk, and never expected such a deadly threat.\n\n[asker_nameDef] wants you to keep [asker_objective] safe at [map_definite] for a few hours until [asker_possessive] shuttle can come pick [asker_objective] up. [asker_pronoun] promises not to be offended by your body odors or lack of manners.\n\n[asker_pronoun] will bestow [royalFavorReward] [asker_faction_royalFavorLabel] on whoever accepts this quest. This is enough favor to receive the royal title of Yeoman, and all benefits that come with it - including a psychic amplifier.</li>
  -->
  <Intro_Wimp.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings>
    <li>questDescription->[asker_faction_name]的一名[asker_royalTitleInCurrentFaction]，[asker_nameFull]正在附近聯繫我們。 [asker_possessive]守衛在一次襲擊中被殺。[asker_pronoun]逃脫了，但現在正在追捕[animalKindDef_label]。\n\n[asker_nameDef]希望你將[asker_objective]在[map_definite]的安全狀態保持幾個小時，直到[asker_possessive]太空梭可以接送[asker_objective]\n\n[asker_pronoun]會向接受此任務的任何人贈送[royalFavorReward] [asker_faction_royalFavorLabel]。這足以獲得Yeoman的王室頭銜，以及隨之而來的所有好處-包括第一階的心靈能力。</li>
  </Intro_Wimp.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings>
  <!-- EN:
    <li>questName->the [adjAny] [asker_royalTitleInCurrentFaction]</li>
    <li>adjAny->hunted</li>
    <li>adjAny->fleeing</li>
    <li>adjAny->solitary</li>
    <li>adjAny->ambushed</li>
  -->
  <Intro_Wimp.questNameRules.rulesStrings>
    <li>questName->[adjAny][asker_royalTitleInCurrentFaction]</li>
    <li>adjAny->獵殺</li>
    <li>adjAny->逃跑</li>
    <li>adjAny->獨居</li>
    <li>adjAny->伏擊</li>
  </Intro_Wimp.questNameRules.rulesStrings>
  <!-- EN: [animalKindDef_label] arrived -->
  <Intro_Wimp.LetterLabelAnimalArrived.slateRef>[animalKindDef_label]已抵達</Intro_Wimp.LetterLabelAnimalArrived.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: The [animalKindDef_label] that [asker_nameDef] was fleeing has arrived.\n\nIt turned out to be quite gentle and not aggressive at all. -->
  <Intro_Wimp.LetterTextAnimalArrived.slateRef>追逐[asker_nameDef]的那個“危險致命”的[animalKindDef_label]已經抵達。\n\n結果它看起來很溫和，一點也不兇暴！</Intro_Wimp.LetterTextAnimalArrived.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: Manhunting [animalKindDef_label] -->
  <Intro_Wimp.LetterLabelAngryAnimal.slateRef>狂暴的[animalKindDef_label]</Intro_Wimp.LetterLabelAngryAnimal.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: The [animalKindDef_label] which was following [asker_nameFull] has arrived in the area. -->
  <Intro_Wimp.LetterTextAngryAnimal.slateRef>狂暴的[animalKindDef_label]是為追逐[asker_nameFull]而來。\n\n雖然看起來很弱，但是其行動力卻出人意料的強。</Intro_Wimp.LetterTextAngryAnimal.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: Should depart on shuttle -->
  <Intro_Wimp.InspectStringDepartShuttle.slateRef>應該乘坐太空梭出發</Intro_Wimp.InspectStringDepartShuttle.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: Shuttle arrived -->
  <Intro_Wimp.LetterLabelShuttleArrived.slateRef>太空梭已抵達</Intro_Wimp.LetterLabelShuttleArrived.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: The shuttle has arrived to collect [asker_nameDef]. -->
  <Intro_Wimp.LetterTextShuttleArrived.slateRef>前來迎接[asker_nameDef]的太空梭已抵達。</Intro_Wimp.LetterTextShuttleArrived.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: Guest died: {SUBJECT_definite} -->
  <Intro_Wimp.LetterLabelGuestDied.slateRef>訪客已死亡：{SUBJECT_definite}</Intro_Wimp.LetterLabelGuestDied.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: {SUBJECT_definite}, who you were charged to protect, has died. [failLetterEndingCommon] -->
  <Intro_Wimp.LetterTextGuestDied.slateRef>需要你小心保護的{SUBJECT_definite}已經死亡。[failLetterEndingCommon]</Intro_Wimp.LetterTextGuestDied.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: Unauthorized surgery: {SUBJECT_definite} -->
  <Intro_Wimp.LetterLabelUnauthorizedSurgery.slateRef>未授權手術：{SUBJECT_definite}</Intro_Wimp.LetterLabelUnauthorizedSurgery.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: Unauthorized, violating surgery has been performed on {SUBJECT_definite}, who you were charged to protect. Because of this violation, [asker_pronoun] will now attempt to leave. [failLetterEndingCommon] -->
  <Intro_Wimp.LetterTextUnauthorizedSurgery.slateRef>需要你小心保護的{SUBJECT_definite}接受了一次未授權的額外手術。因為你違規在先，[asker_pronoun]將要離開此處。[failLetterEndingCommon]</Intro_Wimp.LetterTextUnauthorizedSurgery.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: Captured: {SUBJECT_definite} -->
  <Intro_Wimp.LetterLabelCaptured.slateRef>已被俘：{SUBJECT_definite}</Intro_Wimp.LetterLabelCaptured.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: {SUBJECT_definite}, who you were charged to host, has been arrested. [failLetterEndingCommon] -->
  <Intro_Wimp.LetterTextCaptured.slateRef>需要你小心保護的{SUBJECT_definite}已被俘虜。[failLetterEndingCommon]</Intro_Wimp.LetterTextCaptured.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: Guest lost: {SUBJECT_definite} -->
  <Intro_Wimp.LetterLabelGuestLost.slateRef>訪客失蹤：{SUBJECT_definite}</Intro_Wimp.LetterLabelGuestLost.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: {SUBJECT_definite}, who you were charged to protect, has left the designated settlement. [failLetterEndingCommon] -->
  <Intro_Wimp.LetterTextGuestLost.slateRef>需要你小心保護的{SUBJECT_definite}從你的殖民地失蹤了。[failLetterEndingCommon]</Intro_Wimp.LetterTextGuestLost.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: Shuttle destroyed -->
  <Intro_Wimp.LetterLabelShuttleDestroyed.slateRef>太空梭被毀</Intro_Wimp.LetterLabelShuttleDestroyed.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: The shuttle sent to collect [asker_nameDef] has been destroyed. [asker_pronoun] will now leave on foot. [failLetterEndingCommon] -->
  <Intro_Wimp.LetterTextShuttleDestroyed.slateRef>前來迎接[asker_nameDef]的太空梭已被毀。[asker_pronoun]現在只能走回去了。[failLetterEndingCommon]</Intro_Wimp.LetterTextShuttleDestroyed.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: Quest failed: [resolvedQuestName] -->
  <Intro_Wimp.LetterLabelQuestFailed.slateRef>任務失敗：[resolvedQuestName]</Intro_Wimp.LetterLabelQuestFailed.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: The shuttle sent to collect [asker_nameDef] has departed without [asker_objective]. [asker_pronoun] will now leave on foot. [failLetterEndingCommon] -->
  <Intro_Wimp.LetterTextQuestFailed.slateRef>前來迎接[asker_nameDef]的太空梭在離開時因為一些原因落下了[asker_objective]。[asker_pronoun]現在只能走回去了。[failLetterEndingCommon]</Intro_Wimp.LetterTextQuestFailed.slateRef>
  
</LanguageData>